Definition context_sepcon (Phi Psi: context): context := fun z => exists x y, z = x * y /\ Phi |-- x /\ Psi |-- y.

Definition context_sepcon_included_r (Phi1 Psi: context): context -> Prop := fun Phi2 => Included _ (context_sepcon Phi1 Phi2) Psi.
